adGenAosMefPerEvcPerfHistoryMib.description: This MIB module defines high capacity performance statistics per EVC within an AOS product. Copyright (C) ADTRAN, Inc. (2014).

adMefPerEvcPhCurTable.name: adMefPerEvcPhCurTable
adMefPerEvcPhCurTable.description: This table contains current performance history information that has been recorded since the last 15 minute interval ended and from when the last 1 day interval ended. This table is indexed by adMefPerEvcPhCurEvcNameFixedLen.

adMefPerEvcPhCurEntry.name: adMefPerEvcPhCurEntry
adMefPerEvcPhCurEntry.description: This specifies the information contained in one entry of the adMefPerEvcPhCurTable. It is indexed by an EVC's adMefPerEvcPhCurEvcNameFixedLen.

adMefPerEvcPhCurEvcNameFixedLen.name: adMefPerEvcPhCurEvcNameFixedLen
adMefPerEvcPhCurEvcNameFixedLen.description: The name of the EVC. This string is padded at the end with 0x00 so that this table index has a fixed length of characters of the specified SIZE.
